		(property "Description_1" "The Zynq®-7000 family is based on the Xilinx SoC architecture. These products integrate a feature-rich dual-core or single-core ARM®\nCortex™-A9 based processing system (PS) and 28 nm Xilinx programmable logic (PL) in a single device. The ARM Cortex-A9 CPUs are\nthe heart of the PS and also include on-chip memory, external memory interfaces, and a rich set of peripheral connectivity interfaces."
			(at 36.83 73.66 0)
